data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to Step inside this charming property that just hit the market in East Columbus. Ideal for first-time homebuyers. This beauty has 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bath, providing perfect space for a growing family. The roof is only 2 years old.Beautiful backyard, plus the 2 storage buildings will remain. Ring doorbell with 3 cameras will stay. This property is a MUST SEE!!!
